&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/r/error-in-if/"&gt;error-in-if&lt;/a&gt; — condition is missing or length zero&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/r/non-vector-argument/"&gt;non-vector-argument&lt;/a&gt; — value cannot be used as logical&lt;/li&gt;
